result.name: Winning Restaurant

reviews.text: The food was tasty until the time we found a cooked insect in our food. I told them but it didn't seem to have an issue. If you want tasty food but you don't care if you find "other" than what you order in your plate it is fine. If not, then you have to try something else.

Cheap and fast, as expected of a light restaurant. 
Bonus points for having an English menu for the set breakfast set menu and the main menu (for some reason they don't have the lunch set menu translated.)
food is tasty..and it wont take you long to wait for your  order..
I great place to eat near the hotel
Only if you are looking for a quick and cheap supper.
